_sText:
****THIS IS THE UPDATED VERSION OF THE ORIGINAL FY_WATERWORKS****

--------------------------------------------------------------

Fixed some fps problems by optimizing the map 
Fixed some minor bugs
Added some more detail to the map

Not any major changes with exception for the fps fix

I am aware that not everyone will get a constant 80 fps playing on this map, but detail come at a price. I asked my friend to test this on a really shitty computer, and he got a minimum of 35 fps :P
I guess thats what differs this from many other gg or fy maps out there. 

-------------------------------------------------------------

Hello everyone, and thanks for checking out my map! :D

This is the first map I am uploading, so if there's something you would like to me to know or change about the map, just post it in the comments.

I made this map because I am tired of playing gungame, fightyard and aim on maps that isn't very detailed or realistic. 
However, this map is, (imo :P) and have put alot of effort into making it so.

I couldn't really decide if this was a "fy", "aim" or "gg" map but I guess It can be used for any of them. 

I hope you will enjoy this map as much as me and my friends did!
Have fun and gimme lots of feedback!

---------------------------------------------------------------

Some features are 

64 player spawn 
Moving water that affects physics and players
3d skybox
Soundscapes

---------------------------------------------------------------

Install by extracting the bsp file to your counter-strike source/cstrike/maps
